;  In Omnis v3.3 combo boxes inside tab pane do not receive evAfter event when clicking on a user button
;  as a work around, we load our variables from the contents of the fields
Calculate cvFindText as findTextRef.$contents
Calculate cvReplaceText as replaceTextRef.$contents
Calculate cvFindObj.$text as cvFindText
Calculate cvReplaceObj.$text as cvReplaceText